ng international markets and customers our people and partners we believe success comes from the energy of our people through living our values of safety respect excellence courage and one team we create an inclusive working environment where everyone can make a difference and give their best our  staff are based at the harbour front avenue office and at tepong marine lubricants blending plant in jurong bp looks forward to another successful  years in singapore and beyond use the contact details below to call or write to us at bp singapore we aim to deal with your enquiries as quickly as possible bp singapore  harbour front avenue  keppel bay tower singapore  phone    fax    related content bp sustainability report interested in a career at bp find out more the bp energy outlook   edition bp global cookie notification we have placed cookies on your computer to help make this website better you can change your cookie settings at any time otherwise well assume youre ok to continue global careers bp gbp    usd     share price feed currently unavailable enable javascript for shareprice s search bp announces second quarter results a solid first half with strong operational performance strong cash flow and considerable strategic momentum read more the future is bright but different group chief executive bob dudley on bps halfyear results and the business outlook a visual guide to q results find out the headlines and the key numbers at a glance in this infographic bps  major projects find out about the seven major projects we plan to deliver this year get the details view the galleries watch the videos and more about bp the world is changing fast and bp is changing with it the mix of energy that provides heat light and mobility for billions of people is shifting towards lower carbon sources driven by advances in technology and growing concerns about climate change were determined to play our part in this transition  helping to meet the worlds need for more energy while also reducing carbon emissions the energy transition search for a job at bp our commitment to building a stronger more sustainable energy future is matched by our commitment to the people who will make it a reality bp worldwide with operations around the world chances are bp does something where you are find out what we do in your country investors we continue to position bp for the new oil price environment with a continued tight focus on costs efficiency and discipline in capital spending we delivered strong operational performance in the first half of  and have considerable strategic momentum coming into the rest of the year and  with rising production from our new upstream projects and marketing growth in the downstream  bob dudley group chief executive results and webcast investors section also on bpcom advancing the energy transition our industry is changing faster than at any time in our life time in bp we will help drive this transition – and our business will be transformed by it bp statistical review of world energy the  review was launched on  june with a live webcast hosted by lamar mckay and spencer dale download the materials or watch the webcast replay press releases please select a filter andor a date range  august  second quarter  results  july  bp target neutral expands carbon offset portfolio  june  bp q  exploration highlights full press release listing key documents statistical review  pdf  mb q  results pdf  kb annual report and f  pdf  mb sustainability report  pdf  mb energy outlook pdf  kb country websites united states united kingdom india germany full bp worldwide listing most frequent searches careers at bp gas and credit cards us contact information statistical review of world energy dividend information bp global